Class Behaviours

    java.lang.Iterable<Behaviour>

    public class Behaviours
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Behaviour>
    A thin wrapper for java.util.ArrayList<Behaviour> that does not allow nulls to be added.

    Tan Wei Li, Kee Pei Jiin
